          "_name": "article19",
          "_sourceTheme": "startm5",
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"article07\" group=\"Article\" data-bg-video=\"{{bg.type == 'video' && bg.value.url}}\" mbr-class=\"{\n  'mbr-fullscreen': fullScreen,\n  'mbr-parallax-background': bg.parallax}\">\n  <mbr-parameters>\n    <header>Size</header>\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Screen\" name=\"fullScreen\">\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\">\n    <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"5\">\n    <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"5\">\n    <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Content Width\" name=\"contentWidth\" min=\"8\" max=\"12\" step=\"1\" value=\"10\">\n    <header>Show/Hide</header>\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showTitle\" checked>\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Subtitle\" name=\"showSubtitle\">\n    <input type=\"color\" name=\"iconColor\" title=\"Color\" value=\"#cbc8e9\">\n    <input type=\"color\" title=\"Wrap Bg\" name=\"wrapBgColor\" value=\"#ffffff\">\n    <header>Background</header>\n    <fieldset type=\"background\" name=\"bg\" parallax>\n      <input type=\"image\" title=\"Image\" value=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/cde-blog-header-1800-x-1000-px-1-1800x.jpeg\" parallax selected>\n      <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" value=\"#edefeb\">\n      <input type=\"video\" title=\"Video\" value=\"https://vimeo.com/428046504\">\n    </fieldset>\n    <header condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">Fallback Image</header>\n    <input type=\"image\" title=\"Fallback Image\" value=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/background1.jpg\" name=\"fallBackImage\" condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Overlay\" name=\"overlay\" condition=\"bg.type !== 'color'\" checked>\n    <input type=\"color\" title=\"Overlay Color\" name=\"overlayColor\" value=\"#ffffff\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n    <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Opacity\" name=\"overlayOpacity\" min=\"0\" max=\"1\" step=\"0.1\" value=\"0.3\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n  </mbr-parameters>\n\n  <div class=\"mbr-fallback-image disabled\" mbr-if=\"bg.type == 'video'\"></div>\n  <div class=\"mbr-overlay\" mbr-if=\"overlay && bg.type!== 'color'\" mbr-style=\"{'opacity': overlayOpacity, 'background-color': overlayColor}\">\n  </div>\n  <div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n    <div class=\"row justify-content-center\">\n      <div class=\"card col-md-12 col-lg-{{contentWidth}}\">\n        <div class=\"card-wrapper\">\n          <div class=\"col-12 content-head mt-3\" mbr-if=\"showSubtitle || showTitle\">\n            <h3 class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style align-center mb-0\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title\"><b>Fő parancsok Blockly-hoz:</b></h3>\n            <h5 class=\"mbr-section-subtitle mbr-fonts-style align-center mb-0 mt-4\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showSubtitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-subtitle\">\n              Press \"Enter\" to add more items to the list.\n            </h5>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"card-box align-left mt-4\">\n            <div class=\"mbr-text counter-container mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text\" data-multiline mbr-article>\n              <ol>\n                <li><b>Mozgás parancsok:&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</b><span style=\"font-size: 1.6rem;\"><i>takeoff / land </i></span><span style=\"font-size: 1.6rem;\"><i>– </i>felszállás és leszállás&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 1.6rem;\"><i>move(direction, distance, speed) </i></span><span style=\"font-size: 1.6rem;\"><i style>–</i> </span><span style=\"font-size: 1.6rem;\">a drón mozgatása adott irányba (előre, hátra, balra, jobbra) adott távolságra és sebességgel&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;t</span><span style=\"font-size: 1.6rem;\"><i>urn(direction, angle)</i></span><span style=\"font-size: 1.6rem;\"><i style> –</i> </span><span style=\"font-size: 1.6rem;\">elfordulás balra vagy jobbra adott szögben&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span><b><span style=\"font-size: 1.6rem;\"><i>hover(time) –</i></span><span style=\"font-size: 1.6rem;\"> lebegés adott ideig&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></b><span style=\"font-size: 1.6rem;\"><i>flip(direction) –</i></span><b style=\"font-size: 1.6rem;\"> </b><span style=\"font-size: 1.6rem;\">előre, hátra, balra vagy jobbra ugrás</span><b style=\"font-size: 1.6rem;\">&nbsp;</b></li><li><b style=\"font-size: 1.6rem;\">LED / fény parancsok:&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</b><b><span style=\"font-size: 1.6rem;\"><i>set LED color(color) –</i> </span><span style=\"font-size: 1.6rem;\">LED színének beállítása&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></b><span style=\"font-size: 1.6rem;\"><i>blink LED(color, times, interval) –</i></span><b style=\"font-size: 1.6rem;\"> </b><span style=\"font-size: 1.6rem;\">villogtatás meghatározott színnel, számú alkalommal és időközönként</span></li><li><b style=\"font-size: 1.6rem;\">Hang parancsok:&nbsp; &nbsp; </b><span style=\"font-size: 1.6rem;\"><i>play note / melody –</i></span><b style=\"font-size: 1.6rem;\"> </b><span style=\"font-size: 1.6rem;\">hangjegy vagy rövid dallam lejátszás&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-size: 1.6rem;\"><i>stop sound –</i></span><b style=\"font-size: 1.6rem;\"> </b><span style=\"font-size: 1.6rem;\">hang leállítása</span></li><li><b style=\"font-size: 1.6rem;\">Vezérlési blokkok:&nbsp; &nbsp;</b><span style=\"font-size: 1.6rem;\"><i>wait(time) –</i></span><b style=\"font-size: 1.6rem;\"> </b><span style=\"font-size: 1.6rem;\">várakozás adott időtartamig (ms)&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-size: 1.6rem;\"><i>repeat(times) –</i> </span><span style=\"font-size: 1.6rem;\">adott blokk ismétlése többször&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 1.6rem;\"><i>if / else –</i></span><b style=\"font-size: 1.6rem;\"> </b><span style=\"font-size: 1.6rem;\">feltételes döntés, például szenzoradatok alapján</span></li><li><b style=\"font-size: 1.6rem;\">Szenzor parancsok:&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</b><span style=\"font-size: 1.6rem;\"><i style>read distance –</i> </span><span style=\"font-size: 1.6rem;\">távolságmérés érzékelővel&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 1.6rem;\"><i>obstacle detected – </i></span><span style=\"font-size: 1.6rem;\">akadály érzékelése&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 1.6rem;\"><i>battery level –</i></span><b style=\"font-size: 1.6rem;\"> </b><span style=\"font-size: 1.6rem;\">akkumulátor állapota</span></li><li><b style=\"font-size: 1.6rem;\">Egyéb hasznos blokkok:&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</b><span style=\"font-size: 1.6rem;\"><i>set speed(speed) – </i></span><span style=\"font-size: 1.6rem;\">sebesség beállítása&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 1.6rem;\"><i>set buzzer(frequency, duration) –</i></span><b style=\"font-size: 1.6rem;\"> </b><span style=\"font-size: 1.6rem;\">sípoló hang vezérlése</span></li></ol>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</section>",
          "_anchor": "article19-1e",
          "_isUserblock": true,
          "_cid": "v7VPeRHHhj",
          "_protectedParams": [],
          "_global": false,
